"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 369px; height: 277px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Low power photomicrograph of an hematoxylin and eosin-stained sample of prostate cancer, demonstrating that the malignant glandular structures of the adenocarcinoma (arrows) are smaller in size than the benign glandular structures (arrowheads).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
